I. Setup Django Envoironment
============================
1. Install Python
2. python3 --version  
3. Setup virtual Env and Activate it
    python3 -m venv .venv   
    . .venv/scripts/activiate  
     . .\\.venv\\scripts\\activate

4. Create a Django project
    django-admin startproject CrossCheck . 

5. Create user/Password for the Django UI
    python manage.py createsuperuser

6. Install Django
    pip install django 

7. Install DB Client
    python -m pip install mysqlclient

8. Install pytest
    pip install pytest

9. Install DjangoRestFramework
    pip install djangorestframework
    pip install djangorestframework djangorestframework-simplejwt

10. Install Schedulers
    pip install django-apscheduler

11. Change Password of a user
    python manage.py changepassword <user_name>

12. Create Migration Scripts for the Models
     python manage.py makemigrations CrossCheck

13. Apply Migration
     python manage.py migrate  

14. Start the Server
    python manage.py runserver
